						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Also how do AOROM games (for example a nightmare on elm street) do the scrolling? they only have single screen mirroring so i guess they cannot use the 2005-Register, can they?</div>
<br />Yes they use 2005 like normal. Scrolling both ways can be implemented even with single screen, like many Rare games do. However when done like this it's impossible to avoid all attribute glitches on the borders of the screen.</div>

					
